OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FLloyds hit as banks compete
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ffor mortgage customers     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Lloyds Banking Group's profits plunged 
OL,6, by 28% in early 2024 as competition    
OL,7, grew for mortgages and deposits.       
OL,9,FThe bank posted pre-tax profits of     
OL,10,F#1.6bn between January and March, down 
OL,11,Ffrom #2.3bn last year.                 
OL,13,FLloyds said its margins had been hit   
OL,14,F"mainly within UK mortgages" amid      
OL,15,Fheightened competition between lenders 
OL,16,Fto offer squeezed buyers better deals. 
OL,18,FThe UK's biggest lender also made less 
OL,19,Ffrom loans to businesses, but more from
OL,20,Fcredit cards and car finance.          
